risonment with monetary penalties for allottees non-compliance with RERA tribunal orders. This move aims to decriminalize business laws and reduce court burdens, making the process more pragmatic and less intimidating for buyers.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/rera/welcome-change-jail-terms-replaced-by-monetary-penalties-in-rera-act/131107305?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-823174/131107305.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "rera"}]}